  square inside the foreground PNGs; otherwise device masks would expose a
  visible seam between the foreground square and the surrounding background.
  If you change this value, also update `BG_HEX` in
  `branding/regenerate-icons.py` and re-run the script.
-->
<resources>
    <color name="ic_launcher_background">#2F5C73</color>
</resources>
